control notes: A comprehensive control program operates at the site (French Military camp) including deltamethrin treated bednets, permethrin impregnated battel dress, deet repellents and outdoor spatial spraying with deltamethrin or fenitrothion. IRS is not used. Larval control relies on drainage. No control is carried out outside the boundaries of the camp.
